<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="義解" xml:id="gsz0744c15shiSengChe"><lb
ed="T" n="0744c15"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0744c15"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000042147">京兆大安國寺</placeName><persName key="A009802">僧徹</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0744c16"/><persName key="A009802">釋僧徹</persName>，不知何許人也。敏利天資，高邁逸<lb
ed="T" n="0744c17"/>類，稚歲聰頴，而慕<persName key="A000753">悟達國師</persName>，若<persName key="A002780">顏回</persName>之肖<lb
ed="T" n="0744c18"/><persName key="A002174">仲尼</persName>也。既而時親<ref type="person" target="#A000753">函丈</ref><ptr type="glossary" target="#g1025"/>，頗見幽微，隨侍翼<lb
ed="T" n="0744c19"/>從，未嘗少厭。窺其門牆<ptr target="#n584"/>，其殆庶幾乎。<persName key="A000753">悟達</persName>凡<lb
ed="T" n="0744c20"/>有新義別章，咸囑付<persName key="A009802">徹</persName>暢衍之。為《如來藏<lb
ed="T" n="0744c21"/>經疏》著《法鑑》四卷，《大無量壽經疏》著《法燈》<lb
ed="T" n="0744c22"/>二卷，《勝鬘師子吼經疏》著《法苑》十卷。觀乎<lb
ed="T" n="0744c23"/><persName key="A000753">悟達</persName>為疏，若<persName key="A009816">左丘明</persName>之傳也。<persName key="A009802">徹</persName>述三法鈔，<lb
ed="T" n="0744c24"/>猶<persName key="A007298">杜</persName>、<persName key="A009819">服</persName>之集解歟？初居<placeName key="PL000000042176">法乾內寺</placeName>，<ref type="person" target="#A009802">師</ref>資角<lb
ed="T" n="0744c25"/>立，聲彩風行，凡百官寮無不奉仰率由。<persName key="A009802">徹</persName>內<lb
ed="T" n="0744c26"/>外<ptr type="glossary" target="#g32"/>兼學，辭筆特高，唱予和汝<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1026"/>，同氣相求<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1027"/>。尋<lb
ed="T" n="0744c27"/>充左右街應制，每屬誕辰<ptr target="#n1028"/>，升<placeName key="PL000000042361">麟德殿</placeName>法座<lb
ed="T" n="0744c28"/>講談，勅賜紫袈裟。<persName key="A006571">懿宗皇帝</persName>留心釋氏，頗<lb
ed="T" n="0744c29"/>異前朝。遇八齋日，必<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042276">內中</ref>飯僧數盈萬計。<pb ed="T" n="0745a" xml:id="T50.2061.0745a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0745a01"/><ref type="person" target="#A006571">帝</ref>因法集，躬為讚唄，<persName key="A009802">徹</persName>則升臺朗詠。寵錫<lb
ed="T" n="0745a02"/>繁博，勅造栴檀木講座以賜<ref type="person" target="#A009802">之</ref>。又勅<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042410 #PL000000042270 #PL000000042216 #PL000000042412">兩街<lb
ed="T" n="0745a03"/>四寺</ref><ptr target="#n1029"/>行方等懺法，戒壇度僧各三七日。別<lb
ed="T" n="0745a04"/>宣僧尼大德二十人入<placeName key="PL000000042093">咸泰殿</placeName>置壇度內。<lb
ed="T" n="0745a05"/><placeName key="PL000000042216">福壽寺</placeName>尼繕寫《大藏經》，每藏計五千四百六<lb
ed="T" n="0745a06"/>十一卷，雕造真檀像一千軀，皆委<persName key="A009802">徹</persName>檢校<lb
ed="T" n="0745a07"/>焉。以<date when-iso="+0870-12-14" key="j20391692039169">十一月十四日延慶節</date>，<placeName key="PL000000042361">麟德殿</placeName>召<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京城</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0745a08"/>僧道赴<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042276">內</ref>講論，爾日<persName key="A009802">徹</persName>述皇猷<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1030"/>，辭辯瀏亮，<lb
ed="T" n="0745a09"/><ref type="person" target="#A006571">帝</ref>深稱許。而又恢張佛理，旁懾黃冠，可謂<lb
ed="T" n="0745a10"/>折衝異論者，當時號為「<ref type="person" target="#A009802">法將</ref>」。<ref type="person" target="#A006571">帝</ref>悅，勅賜號<lb
ed="T" n="0745a11"/>曰<persName key="A009802">淨光大師</persName>，<date from-iso="+0870-02-09" key="j20388612039214" to-iso="+0871-01-28">咸通十一年</date>也。續錄兩街僧<lb
ed="T" n="0745a12"/>事。初<persName key="A009802">徹</persName>經江論海，<anchor xml:id="beg0745sgsz1"/>勇<anchor xml:id="end0745sgsz1"/>於揭厲<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1031"/>，於<placeName key="PL000000042420">青龍寺</placeName>講<lb
ed="T" n="0745a13"/>貫，既循<persName key="A000753">悟達國師</persName>義意，寄呈所見，蒙迴八<lb
ed="T" n="0745a14"/>十四字云：「觀君《法苑》思沖虛，解我真乘刃<lb
ed="T" n="0745a15"/>有餘。若使<persName key="A001502">龍光</persName>時可待，應憐<persName key="A001598">僧肇</persName>論成初。<lb
ed="T" n="0745a16"/>五車外典<ptr type="glossary" target="#g32"/>知難敵，九趣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1032"/>多才恐不如。蕭寺<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1033"/><lb
ed="T" n="0745a17"/>講軒橫淡蕩，帝鄉雲樹正扶疎。幾生曾得闍<lb
ed="T" n="0745a18"/>踰意，今日堪將貝葉書。一振微言冠千古，<lb
ed="T" n="0745a19"/>何人執卷問吾廬？」覽茲獎飾，悲喜盈<anchor xml:id="beg0745001"/>襟<anchor xml:id="end0745001"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0745a20"/>以<date notBefore-iso="+0880-02-18" key="j20425222043063" notAfter-iso="+0881-08-12">廣明中</date><ptr target="#n1034"/>，<persName key="A008599">巢</persName>寇犯<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">闕</ref>，<persName key="A005228">僖宗</persName>幸<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀</placeName>。<ref type="date" target="#j20428512042851">其夕</ref><persName key="A009802">徹</persName><ref type="place" target="#PL000000042276">內</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0745a21"/>宿，<ref type="date" target="#j20428522042852">明日</ref>倉黃與<persName key="A002039">杜光庭先生</persName>扈從入於<placeName key="PL000000037464">岷</placeName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0745a22"/><placeName key="PL000000036087">峨</placeName>。再見<persName key="A000753">悟達</persName>，痛序艱難。<persName key="A009802">徹</persName>極多著述，碑頌<lb
ed="T" n="0745a23"/>歌詩。不知所終。內翰侍郎<persName key="A009824">樂朋龜</persName>為真讚，<lb
ed="T" n="0745a24"/><placeName key="PL000000042848">鳳翔</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000035989">嘉州</placeName>皆寫其真相。弟子<placeName key="PL000000042002">秦</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀</placeName>之間愈多<lb
ed="T" n="0745a25"/>傳法者。</p>
